Package org.apache.sis.profile.japan

Class JapaneseProfile

Object
Static
JapaneseProfile
public final class JapaneseProfile extends Static
Provides implementations of Japanese extensions. There is not yet public methods provided in this class. Just having this module presents on the classpath is sufficient for enabling the reading of following data:
  • Global Change Observation Mission - Climate (GCOM-C), a.k.a. "Shikisai".
  • Global Change Observation Mission - Water (GCOM-W), a.k.a. "Shizuku".
Since:
1.0
